## 7. Core Architecture

### 7.1 Logical system map

```text
User UI / CLI / Discord / Phone
        |
        v
Urgo Core API
        |
        +--> Context Assembler
        |       |
        |       +--> Memory Kernel
        |       +--> Knowledge Retriever
        |       +--> Active Persona
        |       +--> Tool Results
        |
        +--> Model Gateway
        |       |
        |       +--> Ollama
        |       +--> llama.cpp server
        |       +--> LM Studio
        |       +--> vLLM
        |       +--> remote OpenAI-compatible APIs
        |
        +--> Tool Registry
        |       |
        |       +--> safe tools
        |       +--> read-only tools
        |       +--> approval-required tools
        |
        +--> Workflow Runtime
        |
        +--> Event Log
        |
        +--> Reflection Worker
                |
                +--> Memory Extraction
                +--> Memory Consolidation
                +--> Contradiction Detection
                +--> Summaries
```

### 7.2 Runtime request cycle

```text
POST /chat
  ↓
Create event: user_message
  ↓
Classify intent
  ↓
Search memory
  ↓
Search project/session state
  ↓
Optionally search knowledge/docs
  ↓
Assemble compact context
  ↓
Call model gateway
  ↓
Return assistant response
  ↓
Create event: assistant_message
  ↓
Extract memory candidates
  ↓
Save or queue memory candidates
  ↓
Run lightweight eval/safety checks
```

### 7.3 Reflection cycle

```text
Every N messages or manually:
  ↓
Pull recent events
  ↓
Summarize session
  ↓
Extract durable facts/preferences/project decisions
  ↓
Merge duplicates
  ↓
Detect contradictions
  ↓
Update confidence/importance
  ↓
Generate reflection report
  ↓
Save consolidated memories
```

